WEBVTT

00:09.970 --> 00:11.792
En hva'? Haa.

00:11.875 --> 00:14.958
- Hov-ho-ho!

00:18.625 --> 00:19.570
Saniteter, vel?

00:20.720 --> 00:21.696
Åh. Pf.

00:22.004 --> 00:22.867
Næ. Mat sita.

00:23.271 --> 00:25.410
Casupa ti. Ova sa ta-ta.

00:25.680 --> 00:27.195
En baba si, ikke?

00:27.284 --> 00:31.048
Esekita! Eh patika. En zizi!

00:31.125 --> 00:35.333
Eh wana ja. Eh sawa ti. En tita pata!

00:36.417 --> 00:37.667
- Coma stjæler.
- Hvad?

00:39.229 --> 00:40.580
Butik Parak.

00:45.334 --> 00:48.000
Åh! se Karik. Saka ting.

00:48.000 --> 00:49.375
Et tonen ecoo.

00:49.458 --> 00:51.083
Eh laka ti na ti qa.

00:51.167 --> 00:52.333
Eh rocka tocka tikke.

00:52.417 --> 00:53.833
Eh yo qure kara!

00:53.917 --> 00:55.625
Nyago siqe klæber.

00:57.818 --> 01:02.125
- Jo pa sa tava!
- Ah, siga stagher.

01:02.208 --> 01:03.458
Også Sepa!

01:03.938 --> 01:05.750
Glorckling startrick!

01:05.830 --> 01:08.083
- Eh para kiri gouratick
- Se passa.

01:08.170 --> 01:11.000
- Katchu en ti-tat.
- Pfft, åh.

01:11.083 --> 01:14.792
Eh sa "åh". B-- Batgar a barsoba, ikke?

01:14.880 --> 01:19.625
- "Åh, se tur, eh patuse"
- "Toure-houre"

01:19.709 --> 01:22.042
- "Ana mor kin en poura doura."

01:22.125 --> 01:23.708
- Marke bou!

01:23.792 --> 01:24.736
En tu-mejse.

01:25.225 --> 01:26.917
- Se det, Danik.

01:27.000 --> 01:28.333
- Åh!
- Åh!

01:29.680 --> 01:31.210
Ooh! Mmm.

01:31.290 --> 01:33.375
- Bo ro lat af en kvaksalver.

01:33.470 --> 01:35.625
- Woah, la ba li bi af Kvakk.

01:35.708 --> 01:41.542
- Åh! Kvaksalver er en kolgid.
- Eh sata ta-ta!

01:41.625 --> 01:42.667
Eh Sinqa Tong.

01:42.750 --> 01:43.958
- Zatick!
- Blugh.

01:44.042 --> 01:44.917
- Ta-ti!
- Zagh!

01:45.000 --> 01:47.375
- Mourkats!
- En ta-tara.

01:47.458 --> 01:48.583
Åh ...

01:48.670 --> 01:50.167
- Krinka!
- Asita!

01:50.250 --> 01:51.583
- Pour le kongen.
- Ma Dante.

01:51.667 --> 01:53.167
- Zaldor!
- Mal Pato.

01:53.250 --> 01:55.042
- Philip Cots.
- Ma Toupit.

01:56.240 --> 02:00.766
- Masiq og nej et bleu.
- Ta-ba ta-ba tou-be di?

02:01.292 --> 02:03.500
Arata, azit!

02:05.595 --> 02:06.958
Øh, åh! Åh!

02:07.042 --> 02:07.486
Oye.

02:09.128 --> 02:10.000
Waha aha.

02:10.080 --> 02:12.125
- Nej, bla, nej.
- Et ca?

02:12.210 --> 02:13.833
- Hov!
- Ja!

02:13.917 --> 02:16.375
- Za Bornak.
- Også en Pasa, et grin.

02:16.783 --> 02:18.917
- Øh ...
- Øh, en masse Shorplee!

02:19.000 --> 02:21.125
- Wow.

02:21.208 --> 02:23.667
- Yo, ho, ho, ho. Åh. Kvak!

02:23.750 --> 02:24.833
Kvaksalver ?!

02:24.917 --> 02:26.833
- Zaba Goth.
- En suba ti-ta.

02:26.917 --> 02:30.083
Ticka sæk. Gå en tincka kamp.

02:35.110 --> 02:37.566
- "Banezinkat"?
- Bada bouta vouda.

02:37.670 --> 02:38.875
Også også.

03:07.417 --> 03:10.040
- Kvak.
